modName: Whitewind Cabin - Player Home - NEW VERSION
summary:
Whitewind is a Medium Sized Cabin that\'s covered in snow & sits way out in Solitary Lands. It\'s Located just beyond Windhelm, on-top of snowy hills, which are constantly assaulted by blizzards and snowstorms.

With its temperatures fallen below Zero, it\'s the perfect location for a True Nord.
descriptionHtml:
Fixes:

- Rear Porch Extended for Smelter.
- Smelter Added.
- Lighting Glitches Fixed.
- Frozen BeeHive and Frozen Bee Ingredient Added  (Respawns) .
- Hidden Armory Key placed near Spare Key.
- Whitewind Weapons added (Eduj and Okin Models).
NOTE: These Weapons can\'t be Smithed & that\'s why they do 150 Points of Damage +50 Crit Damage.

WARNING: If you\'re using my Old version of Whitewind Cabin, please make sure you remove all items you\'ve stored in any containers related to this house, before installing the New Version!

This is my most recent Version of Whitewind Cabin. My first version was empty and  smaller, lacking thought & Originality. 

I\'ve recently updated the OLD Version into this, and now it\'s ready for Download.

If you think this version is too cluttered and overworked, you can always try my old Version here...
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/42249//?

If there\'s any requests or problems, comment and I will try to fix them!

Rate, comment and enjoy.

Peace, xXxSyNc08.
